# 🚛 Transport Management System

A modern **Transport Management System (TMS)** developed to help industries and companies efficiently manage employee transportation, vehicle allocation, route planning, driver management, and trip monitoring through a centralized platform.

---

## 📌 Overview

The Transport Management System simplifies transportation operations by automating vehicle scheduling, driver assignments, trip tracking, and transport records. It reduces manual work, improves operational efficiency, and provides real-time insights into transport activities.

This project is designed for:
- 🏭 Manufacturing Industries
- 🏢 Corporate Companies
- 🚚 Logistics & Transport Departments
- 🏫 Educational Institutions
- 🏥 Hospitals

---

## ✨ Features

### 👤 User Management
- Secure Login & Authentication
- Role-based Access (Admin/User)
- User Profile Management

### 🚗 Vehicle Management
- Add, Edit & Delete Vehicles
- Vehicle Status Monitoring
- Vehicle Availability Tracking
- Vehicle Maintenance Records

### 👨‍✈️ Driver Management
- Driver Registration
- Driver Information Management
- License Details
- Driver Assignment

### 🗺️ Route Management
- Route Creation
- Route Optimization
- Pickup & Drop Point Management
- Distance Tracking

### 📅 Trip Management
- Schedule Trips
- Assign Vehicles & Drivers
- Trip History
- Trip Status Updates

### 📊 Dashboard
- Transport Statistics
- Vehicle Utilization
- Active Trips
- Driver Availability

### 🔍 Search & Filter
- Search Vehicles
- Search Drivers
- Search Trips
- Filter Records

