## ⚙️ Installation

### Clone the Repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/Transport-Management-System.git
```

### Navigate to Project Folder

```bash
cd Transport-Management-System
```

### Install Dependencies

```bash
npm install
```

### Start the Server

```bash
npm start
```

or

```bash
npm run dev
```

